Titolo: Blaze and Blade: Eternal Quest

Anno: 1998

Descrizione: Blaze & Blade: Eternal Quest (ブレイズ＆ブレイド 〜エターナルクエスト〜, Bureizu & Bureido 〜Etānaru Kuesuto〜), also known as simply Blaze & Blade, is a multiplayer action role-playing game developed by T&E Soft for the PlayStation and Microsoft Windows. It is the first in the series (the other being Blaze & Blade Busters, which uses the same engine), and the only one released outside Japan.